 influence the thoughts of others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With this newfound power, your world is turned upside down — offering you the chance to fulfill your desires, shape your destiny, and leave your mark on an entire town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But there's a catch. A mighty power like yours never comes without a downside... </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713690/extras/5cc0593ce8a54a218971ffcbb4d56eb7.avif?t=1772208083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore an open world where each character goes about their daily routine.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's up to you which quests to pursue and whose path you want to influence first. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your harem</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713690/extras/fbb8fc3284ceae4bafd6c8f14ab6ce3c.avif?t=1772208083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the harem of your dreams! Let your girls assist you—have them generate resources, choose their outfits, enjoy intimate moments with them, live together, or even impregnate them if you wish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every girl is unique</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2713690/extras/6a94a9c63e2d3c4630a44837456ee216.avif?t=1772208083\" width=1560 height=878 /></span>Each character in the game has a unique personality, their own story to uncover, and an individual quest line to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every girl, every mind is a challenge of its own. But your power always opens the right doors. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand Your House</h2